BMW May Produce Own, Mini Models in Same Plant, FTD Says

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-09-13T20:32:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/bmw-may-produce-own-mini-models-in-same-plant-ftd-says.html
Bayerische Motoren Werke AG may
seek to dampen the effect of demand volatility by producing BMW
and Mini models in the same factories,  Financial Times
Deutschland  reported, citing an interview with board member
Frank-Peter Arndt.  The paper quoted Arndt as saying large swings in demand
will be one of the main challenges for production planning.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in  Frankfurt  
 jblack25@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  